headline: Intel stock rises as CEO prepares for White House meeting amid Trump criticism
summary: Investing.com -- Intel (NASDAQ:INTC) stock rose 3% Monday morning, paring recent declines as CEO Lip-Bu Tan prepares for a White House meeting following President Trump’s demand for his resignation last week.

headline: Intel CEO to visit White House after Trump called for his ouster over alleged China ties: report
summary: Intel CEO Lip-Bu Tan is scheduled to visit the White House on Monday following President Donald Trump’s call last week for his ouster over ties to China, according to a new report.
